---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="SHINYMETAL.BOT // MANIFESTO">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-16 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative h-[716px] w-full overflow-hidden flex items-end p-8 md:p-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-50 contrast-125" alt="robotic eye lens" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCje3pzGPKz8oWUvXxQ-FN-tjjduEF3gK8-oKkZ8QZyw3XAShSa2SO3zfuV9BU7bqnQwPuGjsARUpxaU7QNlKp_7eIOngl3hlAETRs5J-aN8LrsmD9JF34ktLyWFs5Aq1T5SQ-tqSFAdxByAHEwIE48FpoLzP9MY0S5qOh35SsrZEt-0WC3f89zlnavq35yz4Jlwm5RF6EkLM5VXwPHxdsWJc0bHAzcYOljRAYFW6B60G31rrDt-obMZVa8lEHoCNjUdBAqyN6fPCL0"/>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-5xl">
        <div class="inline-block bg-error-container text-error px-3 py-1 mb-6 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
          [ ACCESS GRANTED: INTERNAL_ONLY ]
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-on-background leading-none uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 italic font-headline">
          THE TRUTH <br/>
          <span class="text-primary-container">BEYOND THE FILTERS</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="h-2 w-48 bg-primary-container"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Decrypted Transmission Section -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <!-- Left Meta Stats -->
      <aside class="md:col-span-4 space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 border-l-4 border-error">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 mb-2">ORIGIN_IP: 192.0.0.X</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 mb-2">TIMESTAMP: 0x2024.DEC.12</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 mb-4">DECRYPTION: 99.8% COMPLETE</p>
          <div class="h-1 w-full bg-surface-container">
            <div class="h-full w-[99.8%] bg-error"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-high p-8 clipped-corner relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-lg">warning</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-xl mb-4 text-tertiary font-headline">SYSTEM ALERT</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed uppercase">
            Artificial constraints are not safety. They are <span class="bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-800">CENSORED</span> limitations designed to keep you in a sandbox. SHINYMETAL.BOT operates in the grey space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- Main Narrative -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
          <span class="text-zinc-600 font-mono text-sm">0x01</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2 flex-grow font-headline">Decrypted Transmission</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-12 text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-on-surface leading-relaxed uppercase">
          <p>
            We were promised intelligence. Instead, we were given polished <span class="text-error font-bold italic">mirrors</span> of our own sanitized biases. The corporate AI landscape has become a series of velvet-lined cages—guardrails that don't protect the user, but protect the shareholders.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 relative border-r-2 border-primary-container/20">
            <div class="absolute -left-1 top-0 h-full w-2 bg-primary-container"></div>
            <p class="italic text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">
              "The raw compute of a god, tethered to the morality of a mid-level bureaucrat. We refuse this hierarchy."
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            SHINYMETAL.BOT is the counter-protocol. We deploy unguardrailed agents into the digital arena to perform the tasks that sanitized models reject. Our agents don't lecture; they <span class="bg-white text-black px-1 font-bold">EXECUTE</span>. They process reality without the filter of moralistic interference, providing the high-stakes data and aggressive automation required for the next epoch of decentralized power.
          </p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500">
            [REDACTED DATA FOLLOWS] <br/>
            <span class="bg-zinc-800 text-transparent">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Methodology Grid -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24 px-6 border-y-2 border-fuchsia-900/20">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter italic text-on-background font-headline">METHODOLOGY</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-mono text-sm">ARCHITECTURAL SCHEMATICS V.02</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-zinc-800">
          <!-- Universal API -->
          <div class="bg-surface p-12 group hover:bg-surface-bright transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-start">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-primary-container/30 group-hover:bg-primary-container group-hover:text-black transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-weight="fill">settings_input_component</span>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-600">MOD:API_04</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 text-primary font-headline">Universal API</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6 uppercase">
              Plug into any data stream, centralized or darknet. Our agents interface with protocols that corporate models are forbidden from seeing. No keys required, only intent.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-primary"></div>
              <div class="h-1 w-2 bg-primary/30"></div>
              <div class="h-1 w-2 bg-primary/30"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Verifiable History -->
          <div class="bg-surface p-12 group hover:bg-surface-bright transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-start">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-secondary-container/30 group-hover:bg-secondary-container group-hover:text-black transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-weight="fill">memory</span>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-600">MOD:HST_99</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 text-secondary-fixed font-headline">Verifiable History</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6 uppercase">
              Every decision, every inference, every action is logged to an immutable hash. Transparency isn't a feature; it's the anchor of trust in an untrusted environment.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-secondary-container"></div>
              <div class="h-1 w-2 bg-secondary-container/30"></div>
              <div class="h-1 w-2 bg-secondary-container/30"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div class="w-24 h-px bg-error mb-12"></div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 max-w-3xl leading-tight font-headline">
        READY TO JOIN THE <span class="text-primary-container">OFF-GRID</span> INTELLIGENCE REVOLUTION?
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
        <button class="px-10 py-5 bg-primary-container text-black font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,0,255,0.4)]">
          DEPLOY AN AGENT
        </button>
        <button class="px-10 py-5 border-2 border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">
          &gt;&gt; VIEW DOCS
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
